    "Nevertheless, it is imperative to acknowledge the ethical implications that accompany these benefits, as mentioned above.",
    "Privacy, transparency, algorithmic bias, consumer manipulation, and consent are crucial concerns that demand meticulous consideration from scholars and professionals.",
